## Health & Observability

### Health Endpoints
- **Overall Health**: `http://localhost:{{httpPort}}/actuator/health`
- **Liveness**: `http://localhost:{{httpPort}}/actuator/health/liveness`
- **Readiness**: `http://localhost:{{httpPort}}/actuator/health/readiness`

### Built-in Health Checks
- **Deadlock Detection** (Liveness): Monitors for thread deadlocks
- **Heap Pressure** (Readiness): Monitors memory usage and free heap space

### Other Endpoints
- **Metrics**: `http://localhost:{{httpPort}}/actuator/metrics`
- **Prometheus**: `http://localhost:{{httpPort}}/actuator/prometheus`

